## 18 Verified Laws

1. Two-Edge Principle (gain > 0.85 + coupling > 0.67/N)
2. Critical Coupling scaling (0.67 × N^-1.06)
3. Cusp Catastrophe (10^8 variance at critical coupling)
4. Hysteresis (0.47, path-dependent)
5. Max-Cut Ground State (sign pattern = maximum cut)
6. Single Attractor (13/16 patterns reachable)
7. Common Enemy Unification (adversary increases honest correlation)
8. Band Effect (intermodulation at 28.2× SNR)
9. Crystallization (variance 0.32→0.01 over time)
10. Re-sync Speed (7.4 steps after coupling loss)
11. Coalition Multiplier (coordinated 2× worse)
12. Consensus Vortex (positive coupling, adversary absorbed)
13. Mean-Field Universality (β≈0.63-0.85)
14. First-Order Transition (energy jumps at gain≈0.84)
15. Dual-Layer Architecture (consensus + diversity simultaneously)
16. Fleet Self-Tuning (converges to gain≈1.15)
17. Cultural Transmission (elders→students 0.99)
18. Generational Drift (decays Gen5=0.41)

